	(29, 'motor_vehicle_safety', 'Motor Vehicle Safety', 'MS0109', 'This course is fantastic', 'This course is written for all individuals that are employed by homecare and hospice organizations. This course is provided as part of a monthly safety education program that has the purpose of assisting employees to learn and understand topics that will help prevent personal injuries, illnesses, and conditions. This course covers motor vehicle safety, which includes {{ user_company_possessive }} responsibilities as an employer and yours as a motor vehicle operator for the organization. This course is not intended to be a course for commercial drivers or a defensive driving training course, which requires hands-on skills performance and being observed by a trained professional. By understanding the topics discussed in this course, you can better take care of yourself and your fellow employees.', 1, 30, NULL, 0.50, 0, '2009-10-25 00:00:00', '2010-04-14 00:00:00', 8, 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, 1),
	(30, NULL, 'Compassion Fatigue', 'MS0117', 'This course is fantastic', 'This course is written for all individuals that are employed by homecare and hospice organizations. This course is provided as part of a monthly safety education program that has the purpose of assisting employees learn and understand topics that will help prevent personal injuries, illnesses, and conditions. This course covers compassion fatigue and moral and ethical distress, their adverse effects, and includes the responsibilities of an employer and yours as a care provider for the organization to be aware and proactive. This course is intended to provide medical information but is not intended as a substitute for informed medical advice, you should <u>not</u> take any action before consulting with a health care professional. By understanding the topics discussed in this course, you can better take care of yourself and your fellow employees.', 1, 30, NULL, 0.60, 1, '2010-04-13 00:00:00', '2010-04-13 00:00:00', 8, 10, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, 1),
	(31, NULL, 'Electrical Safety', 'MS0110', 'This course is fantastic', 'This course is written for all individuals that are employed by healthcare organizations. This course is provided as part of a monthly safety education program that has the purpose of assisting employees learn and understand topics that will help prevent personal injuries, illnesses, and conditions. This course covers electrical safety, which includes the OSHA regulations that mandate employer and worker safety. This course is not intended to be a training course on repairing or working on electrical equipment, which requires hands-on skills performance and being observed by a trained professional. By understanding the topics discussed in this course, you can better take care of yourself and your fellow employees.', 1, 30, NULL, 0.50, 0, '2010-06-19 00:00:00', '2010-06-19 00:00:00', 9, 16, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, 1),
